This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with semantic image understanding and image search tasks. It also uses visual features of images to cluster tags into visual themes. 

The paper also involves natural language processing techniques (word embedding) to measure the semantic similarity between tags, which suggests it could belong to the computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. 

The paper also involves clustering algorithms, which could suggest it belongs to the information retrieval (cs.IR) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. 

Finally, the paper involves image labelling, which suggests it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
